			<div class="book-header">
				<div class="book-name">The Prophecy of Isaias — Prophetia Isaiæ </div>
				<div class="act-chapter">
					<div class="prev-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220520000918/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_59">&lt; prev</a></div>|
					<div class="chapter">Chapter 60</div>
					|<div class="next-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220520000918/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_61">next &gt;</a></div>
